          <p class="ih-pillar-desc">
            The words you use — internally and externally — determine your emotional state, your
            decisions, and how others experience you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ih-pillar">
          <div class="ih-pillar-letter">P</div>
          <div class="ih-pillar-word">Programming</div>
          <div class="ih-pillar-one">Patterns</div>
          <p class="ih-pillar-desc">
            The unconscious patterns running beneath your awareness that drive your reactions,
            habits, and results — whether you like them or not.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ih-nlp-grid ih-fade">
        <div>
          <p class="ih-label" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Uses &amp; benefits</p>
          <p class="ih-body" style="margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:0.82rem;">Tap each to explore ↓</p>
          <div class="ih-acc">
            <div class="ih-acc-item">
              <button class="ih-acc-trigger" onclick="ihToggleAcc(this)">
                <span class="ih-acc-icon-emoji">🔄</span>
                <span class="ih-acc-q">Breaking limiting beliefs</span>
                <span class="ih-acc-toggle">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="ih-acc-body">
                Identify and dissolve the unconscious beliefs keeping you stuck — about yourself,
                others, or what's possible. These aren't fixed truths. They're just old stories that
                haven't been updated yet.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ih-acc-item">
              <button class="ih-acc-trigger" onclick="ihToggleAcc(this)">
                <span class="ih-acc-icon-emoji">🤝</span>
                <span class="ih-acc-q">Body language &amp; communication</span>
                <span class="ih-acc-toggle">+</span>
              </button>
              <div class="ih-acc-body">
                NLP teaches you to read and use body language with precision — posture, eye
                movements, micro-expressions, tonality, and gesture. Improve how you communicate and
                how you read others, reducing misunderstandings and building real connection.
                <div class="ih-acc-examples">
                  <div class="ih-acc-eg">
                    <span class="ih-acc-eg-icon">👁️</span><div>
                      <strong>Eye accessing cues</strong> — where your eyes move when you think reveals
                      whether you're visualising, hearing, or feeling. This helps me understand how you
                      process information.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ih-acc-eg">
                    <span class="ih-acc-eg-icon">🪑</span><div>
                      <strong>Posture & lean</strong> — open vs. closed posture, forward lean, crossed
                      arms — often speak louder than the words being said.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ih-acc-eg">
                    <span class="ih-acc-eg-icon">🫁</span><div>
                      <strong>Breathing patterns</strong> — shallow, high breathing signals anxiety; slow,
                      deep breathing signals calm. Matching breath helps build unconscious rapport instantly.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ih-acc-eg">
                    <span class="ih-acc-eg-icon">🎙️</span><div>
                      <strong>Tonality & pace</strong> — the same words said slowly vs. quickly, softly
                      vs. firmly, create completely different emotional experiences in the listener.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ih-acc-eg">
                    <span class="ih-acc-eg-icon">🤲</span><div>
                      <strong>Gesture & touch</strong> — where people gesture when they speak often reveals
                      what they're really feeling about a topic — even when the words say something else.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ih-acc-eg">
                    <span class="ih-acc-eg-icon">😶</span><div>
                      <strong>Micro-expressions</strong> — fleeting facial expressions (under 0.5 seconds)
                      that reveal true emotion before someone can mask it. Learning to notice these builds
                      profound empathy and read-the-room ability.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ih-acc-item">
              <button class="ih-acc-trigger" onclick="ihToggleAcc(this)">
                <span class="ih-acc-icon-emoji">😰</span>
                <span class="ih-acc-q">Managing anxiety &amp; fear</span>
                <span class="ih-acc-toggle">+</span>
